                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="idx-category-card__title">Complete Bikes</h3>
                <p class="idx-category-card__desc">
                    Fully assembled MTB, gravel, and CX builds ready to ride.
                </p>
                <span class="idx-category-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
            </a>

