                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-card idx-value-card tg-reveal tg-fade-up--d2">
                <div class="idx-value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
